## Setup

1. Install dbt:
   ```bash
   pip install dbt-snowflake
   ```

2. Copy `profiles.yml` to `~/.dbt/profiles.yml` and update credentials

3. Run dbt:
   ```bash
   cd ue_dms_dbt
   dbt deps
   dbt run
   ```
